node.text: What if the storm was sent into your life to prove God's presence?

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Steven Furtick on September 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'SOMETIMES WE THINK THAT GOD'S PRESENCE IS ONLY PROVIDED TO FIX OUR PROBLEMS, BUT WHAT IF GOD'S PRESENCE IS MORE ABOUT FIXING OUR PERSPECTIVE?'.

node.text: Sometimes, you’ll look at something in your life and it’ll seem like there is no way out. But God is saying this to you today: look again.
